{"tid":1626073,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班廢青咪風向撚幫兇囉","createTime":"2019-10-05T09:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T10:20:45.000Z","uid":132839,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"19f2873922fb674ae0dc309ccaf46d509943a309","tid":1626073,"uid":132839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:39:41.000Z","msg":"廢青其實好聰明 文宣又得 策略又得<br />\n但你地連<span style=\"color: gold;\">獨立思考又冇</span><br />\n仲叫唔叫廢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我明好多時候都係跟大隊做野<br />\n但似乎大家都忘記咗<br />\n人 係一個獨立思考嘅個體<br />\n無人可以主宰你嘅想法<br />\n不論你係勇武前線和理非 都好<br />\n睇完 自我判斷 思考 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">要以理服人</span></span> <br />\n有人buy你嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">自然會推 會出嚟</span><br />\n冇人認同嘅咪由佢自己沈<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好隨波逐流</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對家捉緊棋<br />\n而我地連揀邊隻棋去行都嘈一餐<br />\n唔好<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">盲撐 盲跟 盲屌</span><br />\n風向撚唔多架 多嘅係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇用腦思考就盲推嘅人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 百花齊放<br />\ncu tn<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人 </span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">還拖！！！</span>"},{"pid":"f6d8f83e05c16d38ca18329949b4a3965d504356","tid":1626073,"uid":101057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"要置頂 雖然標題撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cd649b15b8bdc753db0d306b9821c6a513a6ba","tid":1626073,"uid":132839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:40:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ce55f9d19e284c5cc3ccd3be05bccdc361bf9c7","tid":1626073,"uid":132839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6d8f83e05c16d38ca18329949b4a3965d504356","tid":1626073,"uid":101057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:40:53.000Z","msg":"要置頂 雖然標題撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm